Parameters: WifiAwareSession: The Aware object on which we can execute further Aware operations - e.g. discovery, connections.
onAttached(android.net.wifi.aware.WifiAw.Description: Called when Aware attach operation @B_android#net#wifi#aware#WifiAwareManager#attach_E@ is completed and that we can now start discovery sessions or connections.

onAttachFailed().Description: Called when Aware attach operation @B_android#net#wifi#aware#WifiAwareManager#attach_E@ failed.

ClassDesc: Base class for Aware attach callbacks. Should be extended by applications and set when calling @B_android#net#wifi#aware#WifiAwareManager#attach_E@. These are callbacks applying to the Aware connection as a whole - not to specific publish or subscribe sessions - for that see @B_android#net#wifi#aware#DiscoverySessionCallback_E@.
